Mambobin majalisar dokokin kasar ta Wales, waɗanda a yau aka sani da gajarta AM (Mambobin Majalisar), ba su gamsu da shawarar da aka yi cewa za a iya canza taken su zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan shawara ta zo ne sakamakon shirin sauya sunan majalisar dokokin kasar zuwa majalisar dokokin kasar ta Wales.
Wakilan siyasa na tsoron cewa hakan zai iya haifar da ba'a.
Wani wakilin jam'iyyar Labour ya bayyana cewa kungiyarsa ta damu saboda ya yi rikodin Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu a wajen Wales: A cikin harshen Welsh, twp na nufin dustete, kuma pwp na nufin bæsj.
Wani wakilin jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru ta Wales ya ce kungiyar gaba daya ta yi rashin gamsuwa kuma sun ba da wasu shawarwari.
Wani wakilin ɓangaren na Wales na jam'iyyar mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce ƙungiyarsa ta kasance a buɗe don canjin suna, amma ya lura cewa furcin MWP yana da kusanci da kalmar Muppet, wanda baya ga kasancewa sunan wasu shahararrun yarinya, kuma kalma ce ta Birtaniya don dust.
A cikin wannan mahallin ana furta harafin W na Wales a cikin irin wannan hanyar kamar yadda ake furta U a cikin yaren Turanci na Yorkshire, kamar sauti uh.
Hukumar Majalisar, wacce a halin yanzu ke tsara dokoki don gabatar da canjin sunan, ta ce: Tabbas membobi ne da kansu ke da ikon yanke hukunci game da sunan da za a kira su.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba wa majalisar dokokin Wales izinin canja sunanta.
A watan Yuni, hukumar ta sanar da sakamakon wani taro na jama'a wanda ya nuna goyon bayan jama'a don sake kiran taron kasa zuwa majalisar dokokin kasar.
Game da taken wakilan, kwamitin ya goyi bayan WMPs (Mambobin Majalisar Welsh), amma zaɓin MWP ya sami mafi yawan goyon baya a yayin taron jama'a.
Wakilan sun ba da shawarar wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma samun dukkan bangarorin su zo ga yarjejeniya na iya haifar da ɓacin rai ga shugaban majalisar Elin Jones, wanda a cewar shirin zai isar da wani tsari na dokokin don canza sunaye a cikin makonni biyu masu zuwa.
Dokar da ta shafi wannan gyara za ta haɗa da wasu canje-canje a yadda majalisar ke aiki, ciki har da dokokin rashin cancantar wakilai da kuma tsarin kwamitocin.
Wakilan suna da 'yancin kada kuri'a na ƙarshe kan abin da za a kira su lokacin da suke muhawara game da dokar.
