Wani kifi ya yi wa wani yaro ɗan shekara 13 rauni a wani jirgin ruwa a California
Wani kifi ya kai hari kuma ya raunata wani yaro dan shekara 13 lokacin da yake neman lobster a California ranar Asabar, ranar farko ta kakar lobster, a cewar hukumomi.
