Shugaban kasar Joko Widodo ya yi wani babban mataki na inganta kayayyakin kasa na Indonesia a lokacin yakin neman zabensa, kuma ya kashe kudi mai yawa a kan hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin jirgin kasa.
Amma rashin kudi ya kasance babbar matsala ga gwamnatin Jokos, wanda zai sake tsayawa zaben shekara mai zuwa.
Shugaba Joko kuma yana fuskantar matsin lamba daga tsananin tsattsauran ra'ayi a Indonesia, inda mambobin musulmi suka koma ga tsarin addinin musulunci mai tsattsauran ra'ayi.
Fiye da mutane 1000 aka kashe kuma dubban mutane suka gudu daga gidajensu lokacin da Krista da 'yan Musulmi suka yi yaƙi a tituna da machetes, kibiyoyi da baka da sauran makamai na farko.
