Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga Premier League-faduwa da Chelsea a ranar Asabar ta hanyar yin kwallo a minti na 89. a wasan da aka yi a Stanford Bridge a London.
Sturridge ya karbi wani faski daga Xherdan Shaqiri kimanin mita 30 daga burin Chelsea yayin da tawagarsa ta kasance 1-0 a baya.
Ya motsa kwallon zuwa ƙafa na hagu kafin ya aika da shi zuwa kusurwar mafi tsawo.
Gwajin ya wuce saman akwatin yayin da kwallon ta fadi zuwa kusurwar dama ta sama na yanar gizo.
Ƙwallon ya tafi a ƙarshe a kan Kepa Arrizabalaga mai tsalle kuma ya fada cikin yanar gizo.
"Na yi kokarin zuwa wannan matsayi ne kawai don samun kwallon, kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq koyaushe suna tura kwallon gaba yadda ya kamata, don haka na yi kokarin ba kaina mafi kyawun lokacin da zan iya", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
 Na ga Kante yana zuwa ya taɓa ƙwallon sau ɗaya kuma ban yi tunani sosai ba kuma kawai na ci gaba da bugawa.
Chelsea ta jagoranci da 1-0 a lokacin hutu, bayan da Eden Hazard ya ci kwallo a minti na 25.
The Blues-an wasan ya aika da wani fashewa tare da diddige baya ga Mateo Kovacic, kafin ya canza shugabanci kusa da tsakiyar filin wasa kuma ya yi tsere a cikin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya zo da saurin gabatarwa a tsakiyar filin wasa.
Daga nan sai ya yi wata babbar fashewar fashewa da ta kai Hazard cikin akwatin.
Hazard ya fi tseren tsaron gudu kuma ya kori kwallon cikin raga a kusurwa mafi tsayi tare da bugun hagu na Liverpool Alisson Becker.
Liverpool za ta kara da Napoli a gasar zakarun Turai a karfe 15.00 na ranar Laraba a Stadio San Paolo da ke Napoli, Italiya.
