Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 da suka kalli bidiyon a tashoshin talabijin guda shida sun kalli shaidar da 'yan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da Christine Blasey Ford suka bayar a ranar Alhamis, wadda ta zarge shi da aikata laifukan jima'i a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, hargitsi na siyasa ya ci gaba, kuma masu watsa shirye-shirye sun katse shirye-shiryensu na yau da kullum don sanar da babban abin mamaki na ranar Juma'a a cikin na biyu na ƙarshe, lokacin da ya bayyana cewa Sanata na Arizona, Jeff Flake, ya shirya shi don haka FBI za ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda game da zargin.
Ford ta shaidawa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa tana da tabbacin kashi 100 cikin dari cewa wani Kavanaugh mai maye ya yi mata fyade kuma ya yi kokarin cire mata tufafinta a wani bikin makaranta.
A cikin shaidar sha'awa, Kavanaugh ya nace cewa yana da tabbacin cewa wannan bai faru ba.
An yi hasashen cewa an samu fiye da miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ya ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige matsakaicin yawan masu kallo don CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samun damar kallon masu sauraro a wasu cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna zaman, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yana da matsala wajen auna masu kallon ofis.
Don ba da ɗan hangen nesa, wannan shine adadin masu kallo wanda ya yi daidai da wasan karshe a gasar cin kofin kwallon kafa ta Amurka ko Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wanda masu sauraronsa suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh da babbar murna, ya jagoranci tsakanin cibiyoyin sadarwa, tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 don sauraron yau da kullun, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ce ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da miliyan 3,1, NBC tana da miliyan 2,94, MSNBC tana da miliyan 2,89 kuma CCNN tana da miliyan 2,52, a cewar Nielsen.
Sha'awa ta kasance mai girma bayan sauraron.
Flake shine babban mutumin wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Juma'a.
Ofishin 'yan Republican mai tsaka-tsakin ya ba da sanarwar cewa zai kada kuri'ar da ya amince da Kavanaugh, amma a safiyar ranar Juma'a, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama shi yana kokarin shiga cikin lif don halartar taron da aka yi a kotun da ke gaban majalisa, yayin da masu zanga-zanga suka yi masa ihu.
Ya tsaya tare da kallon ido na mintuna da dama yayin da aka yi masa kutse, yayin da aka watsa lamarin kai tsaye a CNN.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", in ji wata mace.
Kuna tsammanin yana gaya wa ƙasarmu gaskiya?
Ya ji cewa kana da iko idan mata da yawa ba su da iko.
Flake ya nuna cewa ofishinsa ya zo da sanarwa, kuma ya ce yayin da aka rufe ƙofofin hawa cewa ya zo da ƙarin magana game da batun a kan kwamitin sauraro.
Kabel da kuma tashoshin watsa shirye-shirye sun rufe duk sauraron kai tsaye sa'o'i da yawa daga baya, lokacin da za a yi zaben da aka zaɓa game da ko za a ci gaba da gabatar da Kavanaugh ga dukan majalisar dattijai don ƙuri'a.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai idan FBI ta binciki zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar a cikin mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya kasance mai tabbaci ne ta hanyar tattaunawa da abokinsa, dan majalisa na demokradiyya Chris Coons.
Flake ya yanke shawarar bayan ya yi magana da Coons sannan kuma wasu sanatoci.
Zaɓin Flake ya yi tasiri sosai, saboda a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba su da isassun kuri'u don amincewa da Kavanaugh ba tare da wannan binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bude wani bincike na FBI don bincika zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
