Guguwar Rosa tana barazanar Phoenix, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City tare da ambaliyar ruwa (na iya zama mai kyau ga yankunan bushewa)
Arizona ce kawai ke fuskantar matsanancin yanayi na wurare masu zafi, amma wannan zai faru a farkon mako mai zuwa, yayin da guguwar Rosa ke motsawa ta hanyar yankunan hamada a kudu maso yamma kuma tana kawo ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta kasa ta fitar da gargadin ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata a yammacin Arizona da kuma kudu maso gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, ciki har da Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
Ana sa ran cewa Rosa za ta motsa a cikin layi madaidaiciya ta hanyar Phoenix a ranar Talata, kuma ruwan sama zai fara a ƙarshen Litinin da yamma.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Phoenix ta lura a shafinta na Twitter cewa, a shekarun 1950, aƙalla guguwa guda ashirin ne kawai suka ci gaba da kasancewa a matsayin guguwa mai zafi ko kuma ƙarancin matsi a cikin kilomita 320 na Phoenix!
Katrina (1967) wani guguwa ne har zuwa kilomita 65 daga iyakar Arizona.
Tsarin National Hurricane Center na baya-bayan nan ya yi hasashen cewa za a yi ruwan sama na 510 cm, tare da zuwa 15 cm a wasu wurare a Mongollon Rim a Arizona.
Sauran yankuna a cikin hamada a kudu maso yamma, ciki har da tsakiyar dutsen Rocky Mountains da Great Basin, za su iya samun tsakanin 2.5 da 5 cm, yayin da har zuwa 10 cm na ruwan sama zai yiwu a wasu yankuna.
Ga waɗanda ba su da ruwan sama, Rosa zai iya zama albarka, tun da yake yankin yana fama da fari.
Ko da yake ambaliyar ruwa babbar matsala ce, wasu daga cikin wannan ruwan sama mai yiwuwa zai kasance mai kyau, tun da kudancin yammacin Amurka a halin yanzu yana cikin yanayin bushewa.
A cewar United States Drought Monitor, fiye da kashi 40 na Arizona suna fuskantar matsanancin fari, wanda shine na biyu mafi girma a cikin rukunin, a cewar weather.com.
Na farko, guguwar Rosa ta kai ga ƙasar Baja California, yankin Mexico.
Rosa har yanzu yana da ƙarfin guguwa a ranar Lahadi da safe, tare da ƙarfin iska mafi girma a 137 km, yana 620 km daga Punta Eugenia a Mexico kuma yana motsawa 19 km / h.
Guguwar ta haɗu da ruwan sanyi a cikin Tekun Fasifik, kuma ta rasa ƙarfinta.
Saboda haka ana sa ran cewa zai afkawa Mexico da guguwar ruwan sama mai karfin iska a ranar Litinin da yamma ko kuma yamma.
Ruwa a kan sassan Mexico na iya zama mai ƙarfi kuma yana haifar da babban flood.
Total ruwan sama na 7,515 cm ana sa ran daga Baja California zuwa arewa maso yammacin Sonora, tare da damar zuwa 25 cm na ruwan sama, a cewar weather.com.
Rosa zai motsa arewacin Mexico a matsayin guguwa mai zafi har sai ya kai iyakar Arizona da safiyar Talata a matsayin matsanancin yanayi, wanda zai ci gaba da motsawa ta Arizona da kuma kudancin Utah a cikin maraice Talata.
Babban abin da ake tsammani na Rosa ko ragowar sa yana da ƙarfi sosai a Baja California, arewa maso yammacin Sonora da hamada ta kudu maso yammacin Amurka, a cewar National Hurricane Center.
Ana sa ran wannan ruwan da ke saukowa zai samar da ruwa mai haɗari da kuma rushewar ruwa mai gudana da kuma saurin gudu a cikin hamada da kuma ƙasa a cikin yankunan duwatsu.
