Akalla mutane 384 aka kashe kuma mutane da yawa suka yi ta yawo a cikin teku ta hanyar manyan raƙuman ruwa da suka yi ta ƙuna a bakin teku lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka afkawa tsibirin Slawesi na ƙasar Indoneshi, a cewar hukumomin ƙasar a ranar Asabar.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru a wani biki a bakin teku a birnin Palu a ranar Juma'a, lokacin da raƙuman ruwa masu tsawon mita shida suka yi ruri a ƙasar kusa da faɗuwar rana, suka halaka duk abin da ke cikin hanyarsu kuma suka jawo mutane da yawa cikin mutuwa ta nutsarwa.
Tsunami ya afka a kan girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
Lokacin da bala'in tsunami ya auku jiya, mutane suna ci gaba da gudanar da ayyuka a bakin rairayin bakin teku, ba su gudu ba kuma sun ƙare a matsayin wadanda suka mutu, in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar kula da rikici ta Indonesia (BNBP) a wani taron manema labarai a Jakarta.
Tsunami ba shi kaɗai ba ne, ya tafi da motoci, da gidaje, ya kai ga duk abin da ke kan tudu, in ji Nugroho, ya kuma kara da cewa tsunami ya tashi a kan teku mai gudu kilomita 800 kafin ya kai ga bakin teku.
