LeBron zai fara buga wasan Lakers a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Lokacin jira ya kusan kare ga magoya bayan da suke son ganin LeBron James yana wasa a Los Angeles Lakers a karon farko.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan bude gasar a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Har yanzu ba a tantance minti nawa zai buga ba.
"Za a yi fiye da ɗaya kuma ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mai ba da rahoto na Lakers Mike Trundell ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasa na iyakantaccen lokaci.
Bayan wani atisaye a farkon wannan makon, an tambayi James wane shiri yake da shi na shirin wasan Lakers na wasanni shida na kakar wasa ta gaba.
Ya amsa da cewa, "Ba na bukatar wasannin farko a wannan lokaci na aikina".
Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa zai fara taron jama'a na zabe a yau da dare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin taron jama'a biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a garuruwan da ke da goyon baya, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka sa ido kan zaben tabbatar da kujerar shugabancin kasar, Trump ya yi niyyar samun goyon baya ga zaben da za a yi a tsakanin 'yan takara, tun da 'yan Republican suna cikin hatsarin rasa iko a kan majalisa lokacin da masu kada kuri'a za su je zauren zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia a yau, kuma ta yaya za a iya ganin sa a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia zai fara ne da karfe 19.00 na yammacin ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon jawabin Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai tattauna ne a kan sauraron da za a yi a wannan makon na wanda aka zaba a matsayin babban alkalin kotun kasar, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da laifin cin zarafin mata, ana sa ran za a yi zaben amincewa da shi har tsawon mako guda, yayin da hukumar FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Babban manufar duk waɗannan taron jama'a shi ne tallafa wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka ne Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan taro na jama'a guda biyar da za a yi a cikin makonni masu zuwa, suna da burin tayar da hankulan masu son shiga jam'iyyar, da kuma masu goyon bayan jam'iyyar, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
Sarrafawa a majalisa na da muhimmanci ga ajandarsa cewa shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama yayin da muke tafiya zuwa lokacin yakin neman zabe mai cike da tashin hankali, Reuters ta samu labarin hakan daga wani mai magana da yawun Trump wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
Taron jama'a na yamma, wanda bayan shiri zai faru a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, na iya jan hankalin 'yan wasa daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma Pittsburgh-pressen ne ya rufe shi, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
Ranar Asabar ita ce karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe fiye da kashi 40 a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattawan kasar West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben jama'a.
"Alamu masu kyau ne ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ne don ya ba shi damar yin zabe", in ji Simon Haeder, wani masani kan kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA ta nuna halin yaki domin ci gaba da yin imani yayin da suke shiga wasan guda na ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman guda uku, za a iya cewa ranar Asabar da yammacin foursomes sun kasance daidai abin da gasar Ryder Cup ta wannan shekara ta bukata.
Motsawa mai motsi na Momentum cikakkiyar ma'anar wasan kwaikwayo ne, amma duk da haka wani abu ne da 'yan wasa suka yi imani da shi, musamman a gasa kamar wannan.
Kuma ina suke ganin saurin a yanzu?
"Sun yi nasara da maki shida kuma yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka muna da wannan a matsayin wani abu na ci gaba", in ji Jordan Spieth lokacin da ya bar filin wasan na yau.
Turai za ta ci gaba da zama a kan gaba, ta samu maki hudu, kuma za ta ci 12 a gaba.
Amma kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, Amurkawa suna jin cewa sun sami iska a cikin jiragen ruwa kuma, kuma suna da kyakkyawan dalili na jin wahayi, musamman daga Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma dukansu suna da maki uku daga hudu.
Spieth ya samar da kyakkyawan wasa daga tee zuwa green, kuma yana jagorantar misali.
Girman murna mai zurfi ya zama mafi girma a kowane lokaci yayin da zagaye ya ci gaba, kuma ya ragu zuwa mai yanke shawara don ɗaga wasan zuwa rashin daidaito lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu a ƙarƙashin biyu.
Putting dinsa, wanda ya lashe wasan a 15, ya hadu da irin wannan ihu  na irin wanda ya nuna cewa har yanzu bai yi imanin cewa tawagar Amurka ba ta da dama.
"Dole ne mu sanya dukkan abubuwan da ke cikinmu a gaba kuma mu mai da hankali kan wasanmu", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne duk abin da kowane daga cikin wadannan 'yan wasan da a yanzu.
Rami 18 ne kawai don yin tasiri.
'Yan wasa kawai da suka sami maki fiye da Spieth da Thomas a cikin kwanaki biyu na ƙarshe sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, wanda babu shakka shine babban tarihin nasarar Ryder Cup.
