Wadannan sakamakon da kuma yadda suke da makamashi suna kama da gudana zuwa da kuma daga taron jama'a sun nuna cewa su ne manyan masu fafatawa a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa da masu sauraro zasu iya ganin nasarar Turai yayin da rana ta sauka a kan Le Golf National fiye da Freetwood ko Molinari.
Zai fi kyau su yi duka a lokaci guda, a cikin ramin su.
Duk da haka, ya yi saurin bayyana Turai a matsayin mai nasara.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi wasa da Sergio Garcia, jarumin kwallon hudu na safe, lokacin da yake abokin tarayya da Alex Noren.
Bayan bogey daya da biyu biyu a cikin farkon ramuka tara, Spanyol da Sweden sun kasance a kan harbi har zuwa yanzu ba su da damar yin amfani da su.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu taimako.
Kwallan hudu da gidajen hudu suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallo a kusa saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke ba juna, shawarwarin da ba su bayar ba da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya juyawa a wani lokaci.
Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin tawagar da ta zo yanzu, kuma tana gaba da ranar karshe, amma wannan taron na hudu ya nuna cewa Team USA na da ruhun gwagwarmaya, musamman a Amurka, sun rasa.
Turai na kan gaba 106 a farkon ranar karshe a gasar Ryder Cup
Turai za ta yi gagarumin ci gaba a farkon ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup, bayan kammala wasannin hudu da hudu na ranar Lahadi da shugabanci 10-6 a kan Amurka.
The mai ban mamaki duo Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci tare da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods, kuma ya ɗaga maki na Le Golf National har zuwa maki hudu.
Thomas Bjørn na Turai, wanda ke gwagwarmaya don riƙe kyautar da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya mamaye ɓangaren Amurka a cikin wasan kwallon kafa na safe kuma ya lashe jerin 31.
