Fleetwood shine farkon rookien Turai wanda ya sami maki huɗu a jere, kuma shi da Molinari  wanda tare suka sami sunan Molliwood bayan ƙarshen mako mai ban sha'awa  sune kawai ma'aurata da suka sami maki huɗu daga wasanninsu huɗu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
