Justin Rose, ya huta zuwa fourballs na safe, ya koma abokin tarayya Henrik Stevensen a cikin foursomes kuma ya ba da nasara 2&1 a kan Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, wanda aka zaba a matsayin lamba daya da uku a duniya.
