Sau biyu kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, wata tawagar ta samu nasarar dawowa bayan da ta yi nasara ta hanyar maki hudu a farkon wasan, amma a matsayin masu riƙe da yanzu, kawai Furyks yana buƙatar samun nasara don riƙe da kyautar.
