Rigakafin yana koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinmu gane kwayoyin cutar kansa a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Wannan hanya ta hada da daukar kwayoyin garkuwar jiki daga wani mara lafiya da kuma canza su a dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Kwayoyin zasu iya ganin furotin da ya zama ruwan dare a yawancin cututtukan daji, sannan su sake yin allurar a cikin mai cutar.
Wani allurar rigakafi da ake gwadawa yana da kyakkyawan sakamako a tsakanin marasa lafiya da ke da nau'ikan ciwon daji.
Wata mata da ta yi allurar rigakafin, wadda take koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinta gane kwayoyin cutar kansa, ta ga cewa cutar kwayar cutar ta hawan kwai ta ɓace na tsawon watanni 18.
Wannan hanya ta hada da daukar kwayoyin garkuwar jiki daga wani mara lafiya, canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje domin su iya ganin wani furotin da ake kira HER2, wanda yake da alaƙa da yawancin nau'in ciwon daji, sannan a sake saka wadannan kwayoyin a cikin mara lafiya.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky a Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland ya ce: "Sakamakon ya nuna cewa muna da rigakafin da ke da matukar alfanu".
