A wannan Asabar, New York ce mai masaukin baki na bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa wanda ke da jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa da za su yi wasa da kuma wani aiki mai ban sha'awa; kawar da talauci a duniya.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda yanzu ya kai shekara ta bakwai, zai jawo dubban mutane zuwa babban filin wasa na Central Park, ba wai kawai don ganin manyan mutane kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawar da matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda ya fara a shekarar 2012, ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wani kungiya mai aiki na kasa da kasa da ke fatan magance talauci ta hanyar samun karin mutane suyi aiki da karfi kan talauci.
Don samun kyautar tikiti na kyauta zuwa taron (sai dai idan mutum yana son biya don tikitin VIP), mahalarta sun yi ayyuka da yawa, ko aiki, kamar aikin sa kai, aika saƙon imel ga shugaban duniya, ɗaukar waya ko kuma wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don haɓaka sani game da burinsu na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ta samu a yanzu da muke da shekaru 12 kawai da cimma burin?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da yin wa'azi kyauta hanya ce ta gaske ta sa mutane su yi gwagwarmaya don kawo canji, ko kuwa wani abu ne da ake kira "clicktivism" - cewa mutane suna jin suna ba da gudummawa ta hanyar sanya hannu a kamfen na kan layi ko aika tweet?
Global Citizen ta ce tun 2011 sun yi rajistar fiye da miliyan 19 na ayyukan masu goyon baya, tare da manyan manufofi.
Sun ce wadannan ayyuka sun taimaka wajen samun shugabannin duniya su bayyana alkawura da manufofi masu darajar sama da dala biliyan 37 da zasu inganta rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta iya nunawa ga mutane 390 ayyukan da suka yi, wanda akalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka biya ko kuma aka tattara.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, kuɗin da aka tanadar ya kai ga kusan mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
