"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da agaji, hukumomin kasa, da kuma 'yan kasa da kasa kamar ku, za mu iya mayar da rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihi", in ji jakadan Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, a wani taron jama'a a wani taron raye-raye a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan fiye da ayyuka 5000 a Birtaniya don samun ingantaccen abinci ga uwaye da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da kudaden aikin, Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai mata da yara miliyan 5 da abinci mai gina jiki.
