Amurka na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa a matsayin abin toshewa don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Ministan cikin gida
Washington na iya if da ake bukata shiga cikin ruwan teku domin hana makamashin Rasha kaiwa kasuwannin, da suka hada da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Ministan harkokin cikin gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, a cewar Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, sha'awar Rasha a Syria musamman ma lokacin da suke aiki bisa gayyatar gwamnati ta doka, wata hanya ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina tsammanin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne suna son yin shawarwari game da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma bisa ga mai magana akwai hanyoyin da za a bi da wannan.
"Amurka tana da damar ta hanyar sojin ruwa don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa a bude suke, kuma idan ya zama dole, za ta toshe don tabbatar da cewa makamashin ba zai kai kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi magana ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta gudanar, wata kungiya ce mai son yin amfani da makamashi a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta hanyoyin da Washington ke bi wajen hulda da Rasha da Iran, kuma ya lura cewa sun yi kama da juna.
"Hanyar tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha ita ce ta fi ko žasa ta yi amfani da ita kuma ta maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana mai nuna Rasha a matsayin "farar-farar-farar-farar-farar-farar" da ke da tattalin arziki da ke dogaro da man fetur.
Wannan sanarwa ta zo ne bayan da gwamnatin Trump ta yi rangadin da za ta kara fitar da iskar gas mai narkewa zuwa Turai, inda take son maye gurbin Rasha, wadda ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da Turai.
Saboda haka ma'aikatan gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban kansa, sun yi kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin da ake kira The North European Gas Line 2, wanda a cewar Trump ya mayar da Berlin a matsayin fursunonin Moscow.
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa samar da iskar gas mai darajar dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka karfin iskar gas na yanzu zuwa biliyan 110 na cubic mita, shiri ne mai ma'ana.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa, rashin amincewar Washington ga aikin ya samo asali ne kawai daga dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na rashin gasa.
"Ina ganin muna da ra'ayi guda cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki don matsa lamba ba kuma masu amfani za su iya zaɓar mai samarwa", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurka ya gamu da adawa daga Jamus, wacce ta sake tabbatar da alkawurran da ta dauka a cikin aikin.
Babban kamfanin masana'antu na Jamus, BDI, ya nemi Amurka ta guji siyasar makamashi ta Tarayyar Turai da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da matsaloli da kasashe uku da ke shiga cikin samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban BDI bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da kuma shugaban kasar Rasha, Vladimir Putin.
