Sabon jirgin yakin Jamus ya sake jinkirta
An kammala sabon jirgin ruwan na Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na yakin sanyi, amma ba zai faru ba har sai farkon shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin tsarin da ake yi da kuma farashin da ake yi, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An kammala aikin Rheinland-Pfalz, jirgin da ke jagorantar sabbin jirage a cikin Baden-Wuerttemberg-class, yanzu an dakatar da shi zuwa farkon rabin 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit wanda ya nakalto wani mai magana da yaƙi.
An ƙaddamar da jirgin ruwa a cikin 2014, amma manyan matsaloli bayan bayarwa sun biyo bayan aikin mai ban sha'awa.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg-class marines sun yi oda a cikin 2007, za su maye gurbin tsoffin jirage a cikin Bremen-class.
An yarda cewa za a ba su makamai masu ƙarfi, da jerin antiluftskyts da makamai masu linzami na antiskips da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoye, kamar rage radar, infrarred da sa hannun sauti.
Sauran mahimman halaye sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kiyayewa  ya kamata ya yiwu a yi amfani da sabbin jirage masu saukar ungulu har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tashar jirgin ruwa.
Duk da haka, jinkirin jinkiri yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa na yaki masu tasowa  an ce su ba Jamus ƙarfi a kan teku  sun riga sun ƙare kafin a saka su cikin sabis, ya ruwaito Die Zeit.
F125-fregatten mai ban mamaki ya haifar da lakabi a bara, lokacin da sojojin Jamus suka ƙi amincewa da su sanya jirgin a cikin aiki kuma suka mayar da shi zuwa Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da marines suka mayar da jirgin zuwa wani mai gina jirgin bayan bayarwa.
An san kadan game da dalilan dawowar, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci jerin mahimman programware- da kayan aikin kayan aiki wanda ya sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a cikin wani aikin yaƙi.
Rashin kayan aikin ya kasance mai mahimmanci tun lokacin da jirgin ruwa a Baden-Wuerttemberg-class zai yi aiki da wani mutum a kusa da 120 masu ruwa - kawai rabin rabin mutane a kan tsofaffin jirage a cikin Bremen-class.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da babban nauyi, wanda ke rage yawan aiki da kuma iyakance damar da jirgin ruwa zai iya yi a nan gaba.
An kiyasta cewa 7000-tonn mai nauyi "Rheinland-Pfalz" ya ninka nauyin jirgin sama iri ɗaya wanda ya yi amfani da shi a lokacin yakin duniya na 2.
Baya ga ɓarna kayan aiki ma pricelappen a kan dukan aikin  ciki har da horarwa da ma'aikata  fara zama matsala.
An yi iƙirarin cewa ya kai Euro biliyan 3.1  daga farkon Euro biliyan 2.2.
Matsalolin da ke kewaye da sabbin jirage suna da mahimmanci musamman a cikin hasken sabbin gargadi game da cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na gwamnatin Jamus, ya tabbatar da cewa jirgin ruwan na zahiri ya zama banza ga jiragen ruwa masu amfani.
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta karu ne a tsawon lokaci saboda tsoffin jiragen ruwa sun yi ta yawo, amma babu wani sabon jirgin ruwa da ya zo.
Ya yi nadama cewa babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwa a cikin Baden-Wuerttemberg-class da za a iya amfani da shi ta hanyar jirgin ruwa.
