Donggala wani yanki ne na mulkin mallaka wanda ke kan nisan kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Regentship, yanki ne na yanki, yana da yawan mutane 299 200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune abubuwan da ke kawo tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, ma'adinan nickel suna da muhimmanci a lardin, amma sun fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a bakin teku a gefen Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar gwamnatin Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938 wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya afkawa yammacin Donggala a 1996 kuma ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan Ildringen na girgizar kasa a cikin Tekun Fasihin kuma ana ta girgizar kasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, sama da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar kasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias, a wajen gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 6.8 ta afka kudu a Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya mamaye gabar teku ta kudu.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afku a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1100 aka kashe.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7,5 ta afkawa ɗaya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, a wajen Sumatra, kuma ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai tsanani ta afkawa mulkin Pidie Jaya a Aceh kuma ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da mutane ke tunawa da mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami a 2004.
Ba a yi wata guguwar tsunami ba a wannan karon, amma sama da 100 aka kashe ta halaka gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, inda ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon bude ido suka yi zaman banza.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida
Track Palin, ɗan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi bayan da aka tuhume shi da aikata laifuka.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29 daga Wasilla, Alaska, bayan zargin tashin hankali a gida, da kuma rahoton tashin hankali a gida da kuma adawa da kama, a cewar wani rahoto da aka fitar ranar Asabar na 'yan sandan jihar Alaska.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, ya dauki wayar daga wata mace da ta san shi lokacin da ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don sanar da zargin da ake yi.
Palin ya shiga gidan yari a Mat-Su inda aka kama shi saboda wata takardar bashi mai daraja dala 500.
An gabatar da shi a gaban kotu ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana cewa bai yi laifi ba, a bayyane yake, lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda ya tsaya kan batun, in ji hanyar sadarwa.
An gurfanar da Palin da laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin cewa za a iya tsare shi har zuwa shekara guda kuma a saka masa tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma zarge shi da aikata laifi na aji B, wanda za a iya hukunta shi da kwana daya a kurkuku da tarar dala 2000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da ake tuhumar Palin ba.
A watan Disamba na shekarar 2017 aka zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta tuntubi 'yan sanda don sanar da zargin da ake yi.
Ana gabatar da karar a Kotun Tsohon Sojojin Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016 aka zarge shi da aikata fyade a gida, da kuma yin amfani da makami yayin da yake shan giya a lokacin da ya faru.
Saurayin nasa ya yi ikirarin cewa ya buge ta a fuska.
Sarah Palin ta fuskanci sukar tsoffin sojoji a 2016 bayan da ta danganta halin zalunci na ɗanta da PTSD bayan hidimarsa a Iraki.
Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia: Mutane dari da yawa sun mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta haifar da tsunami kuma ta lalata gidaje dubbai.
Wutar lantarki da kuma hanyar sadarwa sun ragu, kuma ana sa ran mutuwar za su tashi a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar kasa ta afka kusa da tsakiyar Sulawesi da ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin kasar Indonesiya, Jakarta.
Ana yada bidiyo a shafukan sada zumunta da ke nuna annobar.
Mutane dari da yawa sun taru a bikin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya yi ta hurawa a bakin rairayin bakin teku.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York
Hukumomin tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a yi ba a jihar saboda wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari kan hanyar keke a gefen West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da kuma masu hawan keke a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, mai gabatar da kara dole ne ya tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas ainihin kuma ya haifar da mummunan rauni tare da niyya, bisa ga sanarwar da aka yi niyya don neman hukuncin kisa a cikin Kudancin District na New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan maki biyu sun cancanci hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardar shari'ar.
Makonni da yawa bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta jefa karar 22-mataki, tare da wasu zargin takwas don kisan kai a cikin hulɗa da tsabar kudi, a fuskar Saipov, wanda aka saba amfani da shi ta hanyar tarayya a cikin al'amuran da ke tattare da aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da kuma lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci ma'ana da tsare-tsare da kuma ƙaddara, in ji aktor, wanda ya bayyana hanyar Saipov ya yi shi a matsayin hassassun, m da lalata.
 Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, dukiya da asara ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, sun kafa sanarwar da aka yi.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun wuce tun lokacin da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a yankin kudancin birnin New York.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan masu sayar da kwayoyi biyu, amma daga karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a cikin watan Satumba na shekarar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata na gaskiya bayan an yanke musu hukuncin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin yakin sanyi.
An kashe Rosenberg-ma'aurata a cikin kujerar lantarki 19 Yuni 1953.
Saipov, daga Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun shari'a.
Ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana farin ciki da abin da ya yi, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomin cewa ya samu kwarin gwiwa wajen kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayar salula, a cewar zargin.
Ya kuma nemi a rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya bayyana cewa bai yi laifi ba bayan zargin da aka yi masa na maki 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare Saipov da aka nada a fili, ya ce sun yi matukar bakin ciki da matakin da hukumar ta dauka.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar furci da kuma zaman gidan yari na tsawon rai ba tare da damar samun 'yanci ba, zai tsawaita raunin da wadannan abubuwan suka haifar ga duk wadanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
A baya tawagar kare lafiyar Saipov ta nemi hukumomin da ke da alhakin kashe shi su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin Tory ya ce ya kamata a bai wa NIGEL FARAGE alhakin tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin mobilising sojojin jama'a a yau a lokacin zanga-zanga a taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban na Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa za su ji matsin lamba daga masu shakkar kudin Turai lokacin da daya daga cikin 'yan majalisar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya dauki nauyin tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa mai zaman kansa Peter Bone ya shaida wa masu zanga-zangar a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta yi watsi da shi a yanzu idan Farage ya kasance sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da May ke fuskanta na sulhunta yankinta da ke da rikici, ya samu karfafawa daga 'yan kungiyar Remain Tories da suka halarci wani zanga-zanga a birnin na su na neman a yi watsi da Brexit.
Firayim Minista na kasar na gwagwarmaya don kiyaye shirinsa na Brexit a kan hanya a kan hare-hare daga masu Brexit, Remainers da EU.
'Yan wasan ta sun nace cewa za ta ci gaba da ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya tare da Brüssel duk da koma baya  kuma tilasta masu yarda da euro da Labour su zaɓi tsakanin kunshin ta da kaos.
Bone ya shaida wa masu zanga-zangar Solihull cewa yana son ya yi watsi da shirin Brexit.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa Farage ya kamata a sanya shi memba kuma ya sami alhakin tattaunawa tare da Brüssel.
"Da a ce shi ne ke da alhakin, da mun riga mun fita yanzu", in ji shi.
Dan majalisa na Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan tsaya a kan Brexit, amma dole ne mu yi watsi da shirin Brexit".
Lokacin da yake bayyana rashin amincewarsa da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe biyu na duniya ba domin mu zama masu biyayya.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a cikin kasarmu.
Bone ya musanta ikirarin cewa, an canza ra'ayin jama'a tun bayan zaben 2016: "Tun da jama'ar Birtaniya sun sauya ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin EU, ba daidai ba ne".
Tory Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns ta kuma halarci zanga-zangar inda ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina cewa a sauƙaƙe: Firayim Minista, ka saurari jama'a.
Shirin Brexit ba shi da kyau a cikin jama'a. 'yan adawa ba za su zabe shi ba. Ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutukarmu, wadanda a zahiri su ne ke yin titi da kuma samun mu a zaben farko.
Ka watsar da shirin Brexit ka fara sauraro.
A wani sako kai tsaye ga May, ta kara da cewa: Ministocin jiha suna rike da aikinsu idan sun cika alkawuransu.
Farage ya bayyana cewa 'yan siyasa za su samu ji matsin lamba idan sun yi tunanin cin amanar shawarar da aka dauka a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Wannan yanzu game da amincewa ne tsakaninmu da jama'a da kuma 'yan siyasa", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit, kuma muna nan a yau don sanar da su cewa ba za su iya yin hakan ba".
A cikin wani sako ga masu sauraro, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku bar 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke kan hanyar cin amanar Brexit, su ji matsin.
