Warren yana tunanin yin takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi la'akari sosai da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa dan dimokiradiyar Massachusetts ya yi magana game da makomar kasar a wani taron yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai sukar shugaban kasa Donald Trump, ya sake tsayawa takara a watan Nuwamba a kan wakilin jam'iyyar Republican Geoff Diehl, wanda shi ne mataimakin shugaban Trump na Massachusetts a shekarar 2016.
Ta kasance a tsakiyar tunanin ko za ta yi takara da Trump a 2020.
Taron da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne taron ta na 36 da 'yan takara, wadanda suka yi amfani da tsarin majalisar tun lokacin da Trump ya zama shugaban kasa.
Wani mai halarta ya tambaye ta ko tana shirin tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da mata za su zo Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya hada da mace a kan mulki.
An kama Sims daga LSU bayan an kashe shi a harbi
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Los Angeles, sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa an kama wani wanda ake zargin da harbin bindiga da ya kashe dan wasan kwando na LSU Wayde Sims a ranar Juma'a.
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge sun sanar da kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, a wani taron labarai da aka yi da karfe 11 na safe.
Sun saki wani bidiyo na harin ranar Juma'a kuma sun nemi taimako wajen gano wani mutum da aka gani a bidiyon.
An harbe Sims, mai shekara 20, aka kashe a kusa da harabar jami'ar Southern a ranar Juma'a.
Wayde Sims ya samu rauni a kai kuma ya mutu sakamakon hakan, in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul ga kafofin watsa labarai a ranar Asabar, a cewar 247sports.
Wayde ya shiga don kare abokinsa kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
An yi wa Simpson tambayoyi kuma ya yarda cewa yana wurin kuma yana da makamai. Ya yarda da cewa ya harbe Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da wani tashin hankali ba kuma an tsare shi a majalisar siyasa ta East Baton Rouge Parish.
Sims matashi ne mai tsayi biyu wanda ya girma a Baton Rouge kuma ya buga wasanni 32 tare da farawa 10 a kakar wasa ta baya. Matsakaicinsa ya kasance minti 17.4, maki 5.6 da 2.9 a kowane wasa.
Grand Prix na Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya nufa zuwa ga lashe gasar cin kofin duniya bayan da stallorder ya ba shi nasara a kan Sebastian Vettel
Ya bayyana a fili daga lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya cancanci Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar cewa Mercedes stallorder zai taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin tseren.
Daga pole Bottas ya sami kyakkyawan farawa kuma ya kori Hamilton daga filin wasa yayin da yake kare matsayinsa a farkon zagaye biyu kuma ya gayyaci Vettel don kai hari ga abokin wasansa.
Vettel ya shiga cikin gidan ajiya da farko kuma ya bar Hamilton ya ci gaba da hawa a cikin ɓangaren baya na filin jirgin sama, wanda ya kamata ya zama mai mahimmanci.
Mercedes ta yi wani pitstopp a zagaye na baya kuma ta fito a bayan Vettel, amma Hamilton ya hau kansa bayan wani abu da ya tura ƙafafun da ya sa Ferrari-mai hawa ya ƙyale ciki ya zama kyauta bayan sau biyu don kare kansa a karo na uku.
