Elite League: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi nasara a wasan Elite League na ranar Juma'a a kan Belfast Giants ta hanyar cin nasarar wasan 5-3 a Dundee ranar Asabar.
Giants sun fara samun jagorancin wasa ta hanyar harbi daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita wa tawagar gida kafin Dwyer ya sake dawo da jagorancin Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita Dundee kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci kwallo biyu.
Wannan ne karo na uku da 'yan Adam Keefe suka rasa a gasar Elite League, bayan da suka doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast ranar Juma'a da yamma.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da aka yi a kakar wasa tsakanin kungiyoyin, kuma Giants sun lashe wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyers ya buɗe a minti na huɗu a 3:35 tare da taimako daga Kendall McFaull, kuma David Rutherford ya bar wasan lokacin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagorancin minti huɗu daga baya.
A cikin abin da ya zama lokacin buɗewa mai ban tsoro, Sullivan ya jagoranci ƙungiyar gida a cikin wasan a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya bar Cownies a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants suna da jagoranci a hutu lokacin da ya ɗauki burinsa na biyu na yamma a ƙarshen farkon.
Ƙungiyar gida ta sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa tare da kyakkyawan burin a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun tafi tare don taimakawa Nielsen tare da ba Dundee jagoranci a karo na farko a lokacin wasan a ƙarshen na biyu, kuma ya tabbatar da nasara tare da wasan biyar na wasan karshe.
Giants, wanda yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su buga wasan gida da Milton Keynes a wasan su na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Masu kula da jirgin sama sun mutu domin tabbatar da cewa daruruwan fasinjojin jirgin sama sun tsira daga girgizar kasa
An yaba wa wani shugaban jirgin sama a Indonesia a matsayin jarumi bayan ya mutu kuma ya tabbatar da cewa jirgin da ke dauke da fasinjoji ɗari da yawa zai iya tashi lafiya.
Fiye da mutane 800 sun mutu, kuma da yawa ba a san inda suke ba bayan wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi ranar Juma'a kuma ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi tana ci gaba da ta'addanci yankin, kuma mutane da yawa suna cikin rushewar birnin Palu.
Ko da bayan da abokan aikinsa suka gudu don rayuwa, tsoho mai shekaru 21 Anthonius Gunawan Agung ya ki barin matsayinsa a cikin hasumiyar kula da iska mai ƙarfi a filin jirgin sama na Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Airport Palu.
