A 1987, lokacin da aka fallasa Hart don cin amanar mijinta a cikin jirgin ruwa mai suna Monkey Business kuma ya janye daga zaben, Schroeder ya yi takaici sosai kuma ya yi tunanin cewa babu wani abu da zai hana shi bincika damar da zai iya zama dan takarar shugaban kasa.
"Wannan ba shawara ce da aka yi tunani sosai ba", ta ce da dariya shekaru 30 bayan haka.
