Sabuntawa game da algeopploomstring: An rage yawan amfanin gona a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka fitar daga hukumar kifi da dabbobi ta Florida (FWC) ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan da ake samu a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu sosai.
A cewar FWC, an ba da rahoton fure-fure masu fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier County  wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Wani tsiro mai launin ruwan kasa yana da nisan kilomita 210 a bakin teku, daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudu a Lee County.
An gano wurare da ke da nisan kilomita 16 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Red Algae a cikin Pasco County.
An bayar da rahoton matsakaicin taro a ko wajen gabar Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a wajen gabar Hillsborough County, na halitta zuwa manyan taro a Manatee County, na halitta zuwa manyan taro a ko wajen gabar Sarasota County, na halitta zuwa matsakaici taro a Charlotte County, na halitta zuwa manyan taro a ko wajen gabar Lee County da ƙananan taro a Collier County.
Har yanzu ana samun rahoton tashin hankali a hanyoyin iska a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier County.
Ba a samu wani tashin hankali a cikin hanyoyin iska na arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
